<p>Honestly, I’m pretty proud of these terrible puns. And you’ll be pretty proud of the various things you make using your Vitamix immersion blender!</p>
<p>Anyway, I’m pretty sure I caught all the times my spellcheck tried to change Vitamix to Vitamin, but if I missed any, let me know in the comments.</p>